description: Gets the currently advertised ARP table associated with the express route circuit in a resource group.

subscription_id.description: The subscription credentials which uniquely identify the Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

value.description: Gets list of the ARP table.

nextlink.description: The URL to get the next set of results.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

circuit_name.description: The name of the express route circuit.
